.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, may, december, march, june, september
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in december##2
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |        2        |   3    |    4     |  5   |     6     |
| Birthday   | march | june | september | december | may | april |

