.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-15::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, traveling, rock-climbing, cooking, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | traveling | collecting | cooking | rock-climbing |

